## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are limited to the sources reviewed, which may not represent the full spectrum of research on women in leadership. Additionally, some sources may have inherent biases based on their publication context or authorship. Further research could provide a more comprehensive understanding of the topic.

